  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Dodgeball Circuit!  It is the not too distant future, and the robotic wars are finally over.  Most of the robotic soldiers have now been reprogrammed to assist in the rebuilding effort.  Leaders across the world have agreed that the remaining surplus of robots be reprogrammed for a new form of entertainment:  a robotic dodge ball competition!  An expert panel of scientists and engineers have quickly developed and installed the DodgeBall Circuit in each robot competitor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your robot!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You, the player, will head to your garage and customize your very own robot.  Choosing different arms and legs will change the attributes and super move of your robot.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/df0e41b89cc850d12cf4e974c9e5fedb.poster.avif?t=1759004567\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/df0e41b89cc850d12cf4e974c9e5fedb.webm?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/df0e41b89cc850d12cf4e974c9e5fedb.mp4?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take control!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master a variety of moves in order to help your team be the last team standing in the multiplayer arena!  The longer you hold the throw button, the harder you will throw the ball.  You can roll, slide or use your jump jets to dodge incoming balls.  Feeling lucky?  Try catching a thrown ball to eliminate your opponent!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/cc05c102ac78a069a5d5cebca1395212.poster.avif?t=1759004567\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/cc05c102ac78a069a5d5cebca1395212.webm?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/cc05c102ac78a069a5d5cebca1395212.mp4?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Dodgeball Circuit!  It is the not too distant future, and the robotic wars are finally over.  Most of the robotic soldiers have now been reprogrammed to assist in the rebuilding effort.  Leaders across the world have agreed that the remaining surplus of robots be reprogrammed for a new form of entertainment:  a robotic dodge ball competition!  An expert panel of scientists and engineers have quickly developed and installed the DodgeBall Circuit in each robot competitor. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Customize your robot!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You, the player, will head to your garage and customize your very own robot.  Choosing different arms and legs will change the attributes and super move of your robot.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/df0e41b89cc850d12cf4e974c9e5fedb.poster.avif?t=1759004567\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/df0e41b89cc850d12cf4e974c9e5fedb.webm?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/df0e41b89cc850d12cf4e974c9e5fedb.mp4?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Take control!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master a variety of moves in order to help your team be the last team standing in the multiplayer arena!  The longer you hold the throw button, the harder you will throw the ball.  You can roll, slide or use your jump jets to dodge incoming balls.  Feeling lucky?  Try catching a thrown ball to eliminate your opponent!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/cc05c102ac78a069a5d5cebca1395212.poster.avif?t=1759004567\" width=600 height=314 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/cc05c102ac78a069a5d5cebca1395212.webm?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157540/extras/cc05c102ac78a069a5d5cebca1395212.mp4?t=1759004567\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
